Note: Helper Functions for Test Result Calculation

Process called "create_real_hot_reload_test_results" that takes master_report as HotReloadMasterTestReport returns List[TestResult]:
    Let results be list containing
    
    Note: Extract real results from each hot reload module
    For each suite_report in master_report.suite_results:
        Let suite_passed be suite_report.failed_tests equals 0
        Let status_message be if suite_passed then (suite_report.passed_tests plus " tests passed") else (suite_report.failed_tests plus " tests failed")
        
        Add TestResult with:
            test_name as suite_report.suite_name
            passed as suite_passed
            message as status_message
            execution_time_ms as suite_report.execution_time_ms
        to results
    
    Return results

Process called "create_real_jit_test_results" that takes master_report as JITMasterTestReport returns List[TestResult]:
    Let results be list containing
    
    Note: Extract real results from each JIT module
    For each suite_report in master_report.suite_results:
        Let suite_passed be suite_report.failed_tests equals 0
